<concept id="concept_h3h_sdm_gr">
 <title>Audit Events</title>
 <shortdesc>Couchbase Server provides rich administrative auditing for over 25 administrative events
  and captures them in output target files.</shortdesc>
 <conbody>
  <p>Couchbase Server captures administrative events such as successful and failed logins, events
   associated with cluster and bucket configuration and with the use of tools that require
   administrative privileges. These auditable events are captured in the output targets, which are
   files in JSON format.</p>

  <p>Couchbase Server generates audit events for the following admin actions and performed by the
   administrators that belong to specified administrative roles: </p>
